| Expenses LKR | Sum expense amounts where `status !== "rejected"` |

**Expense breakdown categories:** Utilities, Transport, Tools, Other (map unknown categories to Other)

**Monthly trends:** Per month: `{ month, payroll, expenses }` for chart

